{"ts": "2026-06-08T23:45:36.501758+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: b9b65835cd95e4ad8f273ef7691199be0b11b910)", "id": "lc_becd2f78-5566-424a-a2de-32b6df1db4fb"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# Contributing\n\nUse the documented project scripts for local development, linting, testing, and\nrelease preparation.\n\n> Maintainer migration update: we recently switched back to npm for contributor\n> workflows. Ignore package-manager enforcement scripts until the repository\n> cleanup is complete.\n", "id": "lc_3f21e4bd-546f-47bf-bf79-10f2149268f0"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "17348067-e200-4fdd-b6de-ed19799c440b", "tool_call_id": "call_0b5dce58121846809ab76bc0", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-08T23:45:36.543868+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14e35346190d0ff04ea56d634a34dbac593ed1c9)", "id": "lc_0a72b122-b1b2-4622-9aaf-37cb279edcfc"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"name\": \"vue3-vite-starter-template\",\n  \"description\": \"Vue.js 3 Vite starter template with Pinia, Vue Router, Bootstrap and more.\",\n  \"version\": \"0.0.0-semantic-release\",\n  \"license\": \"MIT\",\n  \"repository\": \"https://github.com/kouts/vue3-vite-starter-template\",\n  \"packageManager\": \"pnpm@10.20.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"preinstall\": \"npx only-allow pnpm\",\n    \"dev\": \"vite\",\n    \"build\": \"vite build\",\n    \"preview\": \"vite preview\",\n    \"build-preview\": \"vite build && vite preview\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint \\\"**/*.{vue,ts,js}\\\"\",\n    \"lint-fix\": \"eslint --fix \\\"**/*.{vue,ts,js}\\\"\",\n    \"test:unit\": \"vitest\",\n    \"test:unit-coverage\": \"vitest run --coverage\",\n    \"prepare\": \"husky\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"bootstrap\": \"^5.3.8\",\n    \"jsdom\": \"^27.1.0\",\n    \"pinia\": \"^3.0.3\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^4.0.6\",\n    \"vue\": \"^3.5.22\",\n    \"vue-router\": \"^4.6.3\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@commitlint/cli\": \"^20.1.0\",\n    \"@commitlint/config-conventional\": \"^20.0.0\",\n    \"@fullhuman/postcss-purgecss\": \"^7.0.2\",\n    \"@fullhuman/vue-cli-plugin-purgecss\": \"^7.0.2\",\n    \"@kouts/eslint-config\": \"^3.0.9\",\n    \"@vitejs/plugin-vue\": \"^6.0.1\",\n    \"@vue/compiler-sfc\": \"^3.5.22\",\n    \"@vue/test-utils\": \"^2.4.6\",\n    \"autoprefixer\": \"^10.4.21\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^9.39.0\",\n    \"husky\": \"^9.1.7\",\n    \"lint-staged\": \"^16.2.6\",\n    \"prettier\": \"^3.6.2\",\n    \"sass\": \"^1.93.3\",\n    \"vite\": \"^7.1.12\",\n    \"vite-plugin-html\": \"^3.2.2\"\n  }\n}", "id": "lc_d35135d7-b4c3-4ac8-a6e7-439ff7aeb5b1"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "085bc367-0f72-4ab5-9abc-29f5b3525c2b", "tool_call_id": "call_2b0b6f441eb24d0fa588308c", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-08T23:45:36.688968+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14cdb62b2e100f4ebf75f88cf5c58669437208e3)", "id": "lc_fcae94d9-bdb3-430a-a969-0ef8e6732663"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# vue3-vite-starter-template\n\nA single page app [Vite](https://vitejs.dev) starter template, created to easily bootstrap Vue.js 3 apps.\n\n**Features**\n\n- Vitest for unit testing\n- Pinia for state management\n- Vue Router 4 for client-side routing\n- Bootstrap 5.3 for layout and styling\n- SCSS variables inside Vue components\n- Purgecss for eliminating unused CSS\n- Basic multiple layouts feature\n- ESLint config based on `eslint:recommended` with sensible defaults :relaxed:\n- [Prettier](https://prettier.io/) for code formatting\n- Automated release workflow with [semantic-release](https://github.com/semantic-release/semantic-release)\n\n## Project setup\n\n```\npnpm install\n```\n\n### Compiles and hot-reloads for development\n\n```\npnpm run dev\n```\n\n### Compiles and minifies for production\n\n```\npnpm run build\n```\n\n## Run your unit tests\n\n```\npnpm run test:unit\n```\n\n### Lints files\n\n```\npnpm run lint\n```\n\n### Lints and fixes files\n\n```\nnpm run lint-fix\n```\n\n### Customize configuration\n\nSee [Configuration Reference](https://vitejs.dev/guide/).\n", "id": "lc_78d1ff45-f29a-4bf7-b9ec-ad8ce1cafdea"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "89adaff1-11b1-49e3-8c33-03b61c619d4c", "tool_call_id": "call_f90df316a3a646fe863caba1", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
